{"tid":990692,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次整蘿蔔糕","createTime":"2019-01-21T20:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T02:46:22.000Z","uid":130138,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0588bde6475fe65f7feda647cb870b69bd88e831","tid":990692,"uid":130138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T20:54:49.000Z","msg":"問左呀媽點整 又上左YouTube 睇左幾條片<br />\n原來唔係太難整 只係步驟煩咗啲<br />\n如果邊個位整得唔好或者整錯都可以同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n材料: 臘腸 臘肉 蝦米 紅蔥頭 白蘿蔔 粘米粉 粟粉<br />\n醬料: 蠔油 鹽 白胡椒粉 糖<br />\n(其他人會用埋冬菇同瑤柱)<br />\n<br />\n首先 將白蘿蔔切絲 留&frac14;切厚啲粗啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQfDkfR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQfDkfR.png&h=6bb7c938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後將臘腸臘肉蝦米紅蔥頭 切細粒一定要細粒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngHFyA9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngHFyA9.png&h=4d40598b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/okCx89y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FokCx89y.png&h=52e50aac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvbV6Wt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvbV6Wt.png&h=1a9f7058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後 先將臘腸臘肉炒到出油<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7OjgRor.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7OjgRor.png&h=17019f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加蝦米同紅蔥頭去炒<br />\n之後放入碗入面等陣再用<br />\n<br />\n放蘿蔔絲入鑊抄 大概10分鐘到 等到佢出水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTdJwpo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTdJwpo.png&h=9cfc019b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再加返啱啱炒咗嘅配料入蘿蔔絲<br />\n<br />\n然後開始調味 加咗蠔油 白胡椒粉 糖 鹽<br />\n撈完之後開始加粘米粉同粟粉<br />\n粘米粉同粟粉嘅比例 1:4 <br />\n啲粉我會用水開左先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Zrfnw3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Zrfnw3.png&h=a3c73a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後慢慢咁倒入羅伯斯同啲配料到<br />\n一路搞到佢哋黐埋一舊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AemCASw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAemCASw.png&h=822c58a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然之後就可以放入一個盤<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWhFyEo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWhFyEo.png&h=a90bf77f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用大火蒸佢大約一個鐘到 記住蒸之前用保鮮紙包着防止倒汗水<br />\n<br />\n完成喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EMBvbsS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEMBvbsS.png&h=1ac2ba28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13fa597d4175f90dc947fa2948247c02b7eef548","tid":990692,"uid":130138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T21:00:00.000Z","msg":"加左蠔油 所以望落冇咁白 <br />\n好似未得 決定再蒸多陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214a116e1c435e9bf7d9c6e3f51e57855592ad1a","tid":990692,"uid":145466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T21:02:42.000Z","msg":"平夜三更先黎煮蘿白糕，你失眠丫？"},{"pid":"097ba3bde1a6f22bfcdc11d40b32d221bf05e948","tid":990692,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T21:07:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38b2b3c159b9ff437ea66f75bcb666e199e2a3b2","tid":990692,"uid":130138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"097ba3bde1a6f22bfcdc11d40b32d221bf05e948","tid":990692,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T21:07:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T21:09:51.000Z","msg":"可能我落得唔夠多粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a08e5b834b557f167c3c7ce24434a03422003b